FBIS3-32127 "drlat022_m_94001" FBIS-LAT-94-022 Document Type:Daily Report 2 Feb 1994 Brazil Hargreaves To Serve Again as Civilian Household Chief PY0202001494 Rio de Janeiro Rede Globo Television in Portuguese 2200 GMT 1 Feb 94 PY0202001494 Rio de Janeiro Rede Globo Television Language: Portuguese Article Type:BFN [Text] Henrique Hargreaves, former civilian household chief for the president of the Republic, a few minutes ago accepted President Itamar Franco's invitation to return to his post.
